BLOSHOME v1.0 alpha - EN/FR
This program helps you to remote manage posts
and categories of a blog under Blosxom engine
It just need a simple FTP access to your blog
data. Neither blogging API nor server-side
installation are required. You prepare your
posts offline in an internal WYSIWYG editor,
then publish them to the category you wish.
Easy install/uninstall. Have a good blog!
